<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        .container { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; padding: 30px; text-align: center; background-color: #f9f9f9; }
        .content { background-color: #ffffff; padding: 40px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); display: inline-block; max-width: 500px; }
        .button {
            background-color: #a91e6a;
            color: white !important;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .name { color: #a91e6a; font-weight: bold; text-transform: capitalize; }
        .warning { font-size: 13px; color: #666; font-style: italic; }
        .footer { margin-top: 30px; font-size: 12px; color: #888; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px; }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2 style='color: #333;'>Dear
          <span class='name'>{{displayName}}</span>!</h2>
        <p style='color: #666;'>You received this email because you requested to delete your account on <b>Kingdom of Drama</b>.</p>
        <p style="color:#666">We will delete all your private information (name, email, avatar, phone, telegram, birthdate, about me).</p>
        <p style='color: #666;'>Please confirm your intent by clicking
          the button below:</p>
        <a href='{{confirmUrl}}' class='button'>Delete Account</a>

        <p style='color: #666;'>The link is valid for 1 hour. If you did not make this request, simply ignore this email.</p>
        <div class="footer">
            &copy; 2026 Kingdom of Drama. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
